entries.title: Super Bowl Margarita Jungle Juice

entries.description:
Here's the recipe:

BLOODY MARY
2 oz. (60ml) Vodka
4 oz. (120ml) Tomato Juice
½ oz. (15ml) Lemon Juice
4 Dashes of Tabasco Sauce
4 Dashes of Worcestershire Sauce
2 Tsp Horseradish
Pinch Black Pepper
Pinch Salt
Celery
Bacon Strip
Shrimp
Olives
Lemon Wedge
Tajin

PREPARATION
1. In a highball glass combine vodka, lemon juice, tomato juice, tabasco sauce, worcestershire sauce, horseradish, black pepper and salt.
2. Pour mix back and forth into a second glass to combine well.
3. Rim edge of serving glass with lemon juice and tajin/salt mix.
4. Add ice, bloody mary mix and garnishes. Enjoy!

entries.title: Bloody Mary

entries.description:
Here's the recipe:

WATERMELON JOLLY RANCHER FROZEN MARGARITA
12 Watermelon Jolly Ranchers
6 ½ oz. (200ml) Tequila
1 ½ oz. (45ml) Lime Juice
1 oz. (30ml) Simple Syrup
Ice
Watermelon Slice
Lime Wheel
Coarse Salt

PREPARATION
1. Place watermelon jolly ranchers in small bottle and fill with tequila. Leave overnight to infuse.
2. Rim edge of margarita glass with lime juice and coarse salt. Set aside.
3. In a blender combine ice, jolly rancher tequila, lime juice and simple syrup. Blend until slushy.
4. Pour mix into glass and garnish with watermelon slice and lime wheel. Enjoy!

SHINA'S VIDEOS: http://bit.ly/2kAzwaj
